embeds.title: That player doesn't have premium!
embeds.description: In order to view yearly stats, a [premium subscription](https://statalytics.net/store) is required!

fields.name: How does it work?
fields.value:
`-` You can view any player's yearly stats if you have a premium subscription.
`-` You can view a player's yearly stats if they have a premium subscription.

Yearly stats can be tracked but not viewed without a premium subscription
